{"tid":1463762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位連登仔 我有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:09.000Z","uid":258808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f84b83d059003427f0de8ec491f5f53940e68f2","tid":1463762,"uid":258808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"好簡單  <br />\n由69一直以嚟我地嘅宗旨係咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不割𥱊<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">希望大家唔好再互屌 唔好互相猜疑 傷感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n決一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9cf7d366c60aea44e7bf56a59e90ce645093e3","tid":1463762,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"7c9a17d77778136cb785fa3064367f1a0ed2987a","tid":1463762,"uid":258808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1000f8030b1692a38004af15d92c496b9ff702c","tid":1463762,"uid":258808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f